           SHORT="Mailcrypt: integrates strong crypto into your mail and news."
cat << EOF
Mailcrypt provides Emacs users a simple interface to public key
cryptography using GnuPG or PGP.  All messages can be encrypted,
decrypted, armored, et. al. with a few keystrokes within Emacs.
EOF
